					<img class="svg font-size-sm ml-1" src="icons/logo-klarna.svg" replace-to-svg />
					<img class="svg info ml-1" src="icons/info-circle.svg" replace-to-svg data-toggle="modal" data-target="#KlarnaModal" />
				</p>
